  "detailed_description": "The object of the game is to make your pieces constitute a majority of the pieces on the board at the end of the game, by converting as many of your opponent's pieces as possible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can play against a friend or alone in arcade mode with increasing difficulty.<br />\r\nThe game will test you tactic skills and entertain you and your friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDominate the board and climb the leaderboard.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBased on an early 90's game.",
